query:
SELECT v.id, v.formandoId, v.eventoId, v.valorTotal, v.valorLiquido, v.status, 
       DATE_FORMAT(FROM_UNIXTIME(v.createdAt / 1000), '%d/%m/%Y %H:%i:%s') as data_venda,
       v.createdAt,
       f.nome as formando_nome, f.turmaId,
       e.tipoEventoId
FROM vendas v 
LEFT JOIN formandos f ON v.formandoId = f.id 
LEFT JOIN eventos e ON v.eventoId = e.id
WHERE v.valorTotal = 500.00 
  AND v.valorLiquido = 500.00
ORDER BY v.createdAt DESC
